Source: pg-orca
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), cmake, g++, ninja-build, pkg-config, libxerces-c-dev
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/quantumiodb/pgorca

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-orca
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-orca
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: ORCA query optimizer for PostgreSQL PGVERSION
  pg_orca plugs the ORCA cost-based optimizer into PostgreSQL through the
  planner hook and falls back to the standard planner for unsupported queries.
  This package builds the PostgreSQL 18 extension.
